response.overview: After being roughed up by Alpha Girl, a pair of backwoods ex-cons are in no mood for their parolee officer's progressive feminist ramblings. Both men have fantasized about Ms Sommers for months and decide to spike her water! Jessica finds herself in a nightmare scenario as the men overpower her and start exploring her young gorgeous body! She continues to struggle but the chemicals have taken hold making the men impossibly strong in her weakened state. When one puts his hand down her pants Jessica panics and nails both men allowing her to break free. Jessica transforms into Alpha Girl but to her dismay she still feels the affects of the chemicals. She tries to take down the men but they prove to be too much and deliver a humiliating beating. Fearing the repercussions of assaulting a Superheroine they decide they can't leave any witnesses...
response.title: Parolee Alpha Girl (Director's Cut)
